- Run cleantags to remove RCSID's
- To regenerate the man pages, build and run:
  cd sqlite2mdoc && make &
  cd man
  ../sqlite2mdoc/sqlite2mdoc < ../dist/sqlite3.h
  sed -i -e 's/\$Mdocdate\$/Month DD, YYYY/g' *.3
  [add new man pages, fix sets]
